      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted under controlled conditions representative of at least one COU operating point; boundary conditions documented.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro Couette viscometer experiments were conducted at controlled temperature (37 ± 0.5 °C), hematocrit (35 ± 1%), and shear stress (150 Pa) matching the nominal COU operating point. Boundary conditions are fully documented in the experimental protocol on file."
    },
    {
