      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters factor is not required at Model Risk Level 2. The operating conditions used in validation overlap with the nominal COU point, and differences in fluid source (bovine vs. human blood) are acknowledged as a known modeling convention consistent with FDA guidance for hemolysis prediction submissions."
    }
